climatePledgeFriendly.details: Compact by Design (Certified by Amazon) products remove excess air and water, which reduces the carbon footprint of shipping and packaging. The Forest Stewardship Council certified products support responsible forestry, helping keep forests healthy for future generations.

features: GENTLE ON THE PLANET: Contribute to the conservation of ecosystems throughout the world by making the eco smart switch to biofriendly baby wipes, fully compliant with the Forest Stewardship Council (FSC) – which promotes environmentally appropriate, socially beneficial, and economically viable management of the world’s forests.

GENTLE ON BABY'S SKIN: No plastics. No parabens. No alcohol. No synthetics. No harsh chemicals. Purity that parents can trust. Moistened with 99% pure water, our unscented baby wipes are gentle enough for wiping the delicate skin of newborn infants & premature babies.

GOING GREEN MADE EASY: Ordinary wipes & diapers get a bad rap because they pollute our world. Our goal is to bring green products to parents more easily & thus save the planet for future generations. Fully, 100% biofriendly baby towelettes wipes effectively lessen human impact on the environment. Cruelty-free, degradable & completely honest.

RAPID DECOMPOSITION: Unlike other wipes, these eco-friendly baby wipes are made out of materials sourced straight from the earth. Derived from trees, the all-natural viscose material quickly breaks down & fully disintegrates back into the ground in several months rather than 100+ years.

HAPPINESS GUARANTEED: Big, thick & just as effective as traditional baby wipes, our towelettes are sure to impress. We back every pack with a risk-free guarantee. Full refunds issued for returns within 30 days. Place your order now!

reviews.reviewText: These small wipe packets are great to have anywhere. They are small enough to fit in your purse, glove compartments, etc. They are a good thickness and clean well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 9, 2022
reviews.reviewText: Great little to-go packs. Smell great. Refreshing without the harsh antibacterial chemicals. Great for quick face & hand wipe ups for kids & adults. Will definitely buy again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2021
reviews.reviewText: I appreciate the fact that these are biodegradable... But I would definitely appreciate it if they didn't feel like they were going to "biodegrade" in my hand while I'm wiping a poopy butt. They're super flimsy and see through and look like they're full of holes. If you're dealing with a particularly nasty situation you're definitely going to want to use several of these at once. They aren't nearly as sturdy as wipes I've used in the past. The small packages are definitely nice for tossing in a purse when I don't feel like taking the whole diaper bag somewhere, I just wish they were more sturdy wipes.
